MATCH_TOOL: Edit|Write
MATCH_PATTERN: ticker|Ticker|TICKER
ADVISORY: |
  Ticker messages arrive via TICKER.UPDATE WebSocket events (their own namespace),
  NOT via SYSTEM.SYNC. Per ADR-030, the useGameEngine hook dispatches ticker messages
  separately. The store field is `tickerMessages` but it's populated by TICKER.UPDATE,
  not the SYNC handler. Don't wire ticker consumption to the SYNC flow.
